*xfce4-power-manager-1.5.0 (26 May 2015)

  26 May 2015; Michał Górny <mgorny@gentoo.org>
  +xfce4-power-manager-1.5.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. The new version switches to GTK+3 and upower-0.99*, has some
  real icon improvements and some icon-related bug fixes.

  26 Apr 2015; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org>
  xfce4-power-manager-1.4.1.ebuild, xfce4-power-manager-1.4.4.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc64 (bug #520296).

  22 Apr 2015; Denis Dupeyron <calchan@gentoo.org>
  -xfce4-power-manager-1.4.0.ebuild, -xfce4-power-manager-1.4.2.ebuild,
  -xfce4-power-manager-1.4.3.ebuild,
  -files/xfce4-power-manager-1.4.0-fix-handle-lid-switch.patch:
  Cleanup. Make sure to keep xfce4-power-manager-1.4.1 as long as bug #531694
  is not resolved upstream.

